<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Inspiring Stories - InspireSphere</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #ffe6f0, #f9f0ff);
    }
    header {
      background-color: #ffcce0;
      padding: 20px 40px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #993366;
    }
    nav a {
      margin-left: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #8a004f;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      color: #5c005c;
    }
    .story-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 30px;
      padding: 40px;
    }
    .story-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease;
    }
    .story-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }
    .story-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 180px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      object-fit: cover;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .story-card h3 {
      color: #4b004b;
      font-size: 18px;
      margin: 10px 0 5px;
    }
    .story-card p {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .read-more {
      margin-top: 15px;
      background: #ff4d88;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: bold;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>InspireSphere</h1>
    <nav>
      <a href="/home">Home</a>
      
      
    </nav>
  </header>

  <h2>Inspiring Stories</h2>

  <div class="story-grid">
    <!-- Story 1 -->
    <div class="story-card">
      <img src="/images/hero1.avif" alt="Story 1">
      <h3>From Homeless to Harvard</h3>
      <p>Liz Murray grew up on the streets of New York but fought against all odds to graduate from Harvard.</p>
      <a class="read-more" href="/story_1">Read More</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Story 2 -->
    <div class="story-card">
      <img src="/images/hero2.avif" alt="Story 2">
      <h3>The Man Who Planted Forests</h3>
      <p>Jadav Payeng planted an entire forest by himself — a symbol of hope for future generations.</p>
      <a class="read-more" href="/story_2">Read More</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Story 3 -->
    <div class="story-card">
      <img src="/images/hero3.avif" alt="Story 3">
      <h3>Born Without Arms, Full of Dreams</h3>
      <p>Jessica Cox became the world’s first licensed armless pilot — flying planes with her feet.</p>
      <a class="read-more" href="/story_3">Read More</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Story 4 -->
    <div class="story-card">
      <img src="/images/hero4.avif" alt="Story 4">
      <h3>Wheelchair Warrior</h3>
      <p>Aaron Fotheringham performs daring stunts in his wheelchair — a symbol of limitless courage.</p>
      <a class="read-more" href="/story_4">Read More</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Story 5 -->
    <div class="story-card">
      <img src="/images/hero5.avif" alt="Story 5">
      <h3>The Girl Who Silenced the World</h3>
      <p>At 12, Severn Suzuki’s UN speech on climate change shook the world leaders into silence.</p>
      <a class="read-more" href="/story_5">Read More</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Story 6 -->
    <div class="story-card">
      <img src="/images/hero6.avif" alt="Story 6">
      <h3>Blind But Leading the Blind</h3>
      <p>Sabriye Tenberken founded a school for blind children in Tibet, changing countless lives.</p>
      <a class="read-more" href="/story_6">Read More</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Story 7 -->
    <div class="story-card">
      <img src="/images/hero7.avif" alt="Story 7">
      <h3>The Shoeless Tech Genius</h3>
      <p>Tanmay Bakshi became a Google AI expert while still a teen — proving talent has no age.</p>
      <a class="read-more" href="/story_7">Read More</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Story 8 -->
    <div class="story-card">
      <img src="/images/hero8.avif" alt="Story 8">
      <h3>Milk Seller to Scientist</h3>
      <p>Dr. APJ Abdul Kalam rose from humble beginnings to become India’s “Missile Man.”</p>
      <a class="read-more" href="/story_8">Read More</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Story 9 -->
    <div class="story-card">
      <img src="/images/hero9.avif" alt="Story 9">
      <h3>One-Legged Dancer</h3>
      <p>Viktoria Modesta became a pop icon and dancer, proving strength comes in many forms.</p>
      <a class="read-more" href="/story_9">Read More</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Story 10 -->
    <div class="story-card">
      <img src="/images/hero10.avif" alt="Story 10">
      <h3>Healed by Helping</h3>
      <p>Kevin Hines survived a suicide attempt — now he travels the world helping others heal.</p>
      <a class="read-more" href="/story_10">Read More</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
